a-core#name-example-meta-schema-with-vo" class=3D"xref">Example meta-schema=
 with vocabulary declarations</a></p>
</li>
            </ul>
</li>
          <li class=3D"compact toc ulBare ulEmpty" id=3D"section-toc.1-1.20=
">
